{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/2/comments/47050409.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:32b0425c9c2c..c385a6addf5c?path=cmake%2FIgnUtils.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/2/_/diff#comment-47050409"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/2.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/2"}}, "title": "Creating project components [Ready For Review]"}, "content": {"raw": "Passing a bool as a third argument does not set the variable in the parent scope on xenial/3.5.1. Only the text PARENT_SCOPE does it. How about:\n\n```CMake\nif(ign_string_append_PARENT_SCOPE)\n  set(${output_var} \"${${output_var}}${delim}${val}\" PARENT_SCOPE)\nelse()\n  set(${output_var} \"${${output_var}}${delim}${val}\")\nendif()\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Passing a bool as a third argument does not set the variable in the parent scope on xenial/3.5.1. Only the text PARENT_SCOPE does it. How about:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-CMake\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nb\">if</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">ign_string_append_PARENT_SCOPE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"nb\">set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">${</span><span class=\"nv\">output_var</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;${${output_var}}${delim}${val}&quot;</span> <span class=\"s\">PARENT_SCOPE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">else</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n  <span class=\"nb\">set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">${</span><span class=\"nv\">output_var</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;${${output_var}}${delim}${val}&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">endif</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-10-12T16:31:13.333728+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Shane Loretz", "uuid": "{656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B656e3311-aad9-45a1-aaf7-b0ee0e84b287%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:684383ab-ac95-4859-a350-4a6f41a94a22/c7a1ebf5-cade-4115-9f26-9d3facb776db/128"}}, "nickname": "Shane Loretz", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:684383ab-ac95-4859-a350-4a6f41a94a22"}, "inline": {"to": 395, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "cmake/IgnUtils.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2017-10-12T16:31:19.968158+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 47050409}